		</div></li><li class="or-side-navigation-parent"><a data-toggle="collapse" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="a34b476f-bd28-4160-9e5a-009cc2e28431" id="0ae7e491-6deb-4870-be50-1d6e077890e8" href="#a34b476f-bd28-4160-9e5a-009cc2e28431" class="collapsed">Future Ready Oregon<span class="or-side-navigation-caret material-icons skiptranslate">expand_more</span></a><div aria-labelledby="0ae7e491-6deb-4870-be50-1d6e077890e8" id="a34b476f-bd28-4160-9e5a-009cc2e28431" class="collapse">
			<ul class="or-side-navigation-submenu list-unstyled">
				<li class=""><a href="/highered/about/Pages/future-ready.aspx">About Future Ready Oregon</a></li><li class=""><a href="/highered/about/Pages/future-ready-about.aspx">Future Ready Oregon – Program Overview</a></li><li class=""><a href="/highered/about/Pages/future-ready-grant-resources.aspx">Future Ready Oregon – Resources for Grantees</a></li><li class=""><a href="/highered/about/pages/future-ready-impacts-outcomes.aspx">Future Ready Oregon –  Impacts and Outcomes</a></li><li class=""><a href="/highered/about/pages/future-ready-industry-consortia.aspx">Healthcare, Manufacturing, and Technology Industry Consortia</a></li>
