   </section>
<div class="ms-rtestate-read ms-rte-wpbox"><div class="ms-rtestate-notify  ms-rtestate-read 582311c0-e0e0-4b19-9250-59a61fa0f0c7" id="div_582311c0-e0e0-4b19-9250-59a61fa0f0c7" unselectable="on"><div id="MSOZoneCell_WebPartWPQ1" class="s4-wpcell-plain ms-webpartzone-cell ms-webpart-cell-vertical ms-fullWidth ">
	<div class="ms-webpart-chrome ms-webpart-chrome-vertical ms-webpart-chrome-fullWidth ">
	<div    id="WebPartWPQ1"  class="ms-WPBody "   style="" ><div id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl40_g_582311c0_e0e0_4b19_9250_59a61fa0f0c7">
		<div class="list-unstyled panel-group or-accordion-list" id="accordion-ctl00_ctl00_ctl40_g_582311c0_e0e0_4b19_9250_59a61fa0f0c7_ctl01">
			<div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-76f2d3f5-d7f5-4b59-ba94-ae740b506dc8">
				<h2>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#76f2d3f5-d7f5-4b59-ba94-ae740b506dc8" aria-controls="76f2d3f5-d7f5-4b59-ba94-ae740b506dc8" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="b0ce468c-268c-4b11-857b-ff3d08b3583a">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Request for Proposals: 25-108-RFA AmeriCorps 2025-26 Formula Funding_Final</p><p class="panel-subtitle">Deadline: 1/29/26 at 11:59PM Pacific Time</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h2><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="76f2d3f5-d7f5-4b59-ba94-ae740b506dc8" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<dl class="dl-horizontal or-description-list">
							<dt>Name of Grant or Contract</dt><dd>Request for Proposals: 25-108-RFA AmeriCorps 2025-26 Formula Funding_Final</dd><dt>OregonBuys number</dt><dd>N/A</dd><dt>Due date</dt><dd>1/29/2026</dd><dt>Summary of Work</dt><dd><div class="ExternalClassDD4A193E295E4E7183CF6C2DE8C314B6"><div>The State of Oregon, acting by and through its Higher Education Coordinating Commission, (“HECC”) is issuing this RFA for the OregonServes State Service Commission’s (“OSC”) 2026 AmeriCorps Formula Funding Grant Opportunity.<br></div><div><br></div><div>OSC is housed within HECC and administered through the Office of Workforce Investments (“OWI”). As the AmeriCorps State Service Commission in Oregon, OSC administers state AmeriCorps Program Grants. This 2026 AmeriCorps Formula Funding Grant Opportunity is funded through OSC’s AmeriCorps State Formula Funding Allocation and provides grant funding for two types of AmeriCorps program models&#58; (i) Formula Cost-Reimbursement Grants and (ii) Formula Fixed Amount Grants.<br></div><div><br></div><div>HECC is issuing this RFA pursuant to its authority under ORS 350.075 and ORS 660.515.<br></div><p><br></p><p><br></p></div></dd><dt>Deadline to Apply</dt><dd>Deadline: 1/29/26 at 11:59PM Pacific Time</dd><dt>Review all Requirements</dt><dd><div class="ExternalClass850EFB0B1CD241DD9277CD89DEB74343"><p>Please review all requirements in the RFA&#58;</p><p><ul><li><a href="/highered/about/Documents/Grants-contracts/RFA/25-108-RFA-AmeriCorps-2025-26-FormulaFunding/25-108-RFA%20AmeriCorps%202025-26%20Formula%20Funding_Final.pdf">​25-108-RFA AmeriCorps 2025-26 Formula Funding​</a>​</li></ul><br></p></div></dd><dt>Support</dt><dd><div class="ExternalClassD8635C66083F467BBD9CB7BD1D0D8BEB"><p>​Email&#58;&#160;oregon.serves@hecc.oregon.gov</p><p><br></p></div></dd>
						</dl>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-4ed06583-40ce-47b9-b62a-838bf7cf2feb">
				<h2>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#4ed06583-40ce-47b9-b62a-838bf7cf2feb" aria-controls="4ed06583-40ce-47b9-b62a-838bf7cf2feb" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="c88ac2be-c79f-4e7d-9d90-250a80f36d57">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Request for Applications (RFA): 25-161 OregonServes AmeriCorps Planning Grant</p><p class="panel-subtitle">On a rolling basis, final deadline: 11/23/2025 at 11:59 PM</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h2><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="4ed06583-40ce-47b9-b62a-838bf7cf2feb" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<dl class="dl-horizontal or-description-list">
							<dt>Name of Grant or Contract</dt><dd>Request for Applications (RFA): 25-161 OregonServes AmeriCorps Planning Grant</dd><dt>OregonBuys number</dt><dd>N/A</dd><dt>Due date</dt><dd>11/23/2025</dd><dt>Summary of Work</dt><dd><div class="ExternalClass223F4515A9C14633841621185DBE4B3C"><p>​</p><div>The State of Oregon, acting by and through its Higher Education Coordinating Commission, (“HECC”), is issuing this Request for Applications (“RFA”) for the OregonServes State Service Commission’s (“OSC”) 2025-2026 AmeriCorps Planning Grant Opportunity. The opportunity is to provide financial support to organizations that will develop an AmeriCorps program that will place AmeriCorps members in service solely within Oregon. OSC is an entity of the State of Oregon, housed within the Office of Workforce Investments, located within HECC.<br></div><div><br></div><div>The 2025-2026 AmeriCorps Planning Grant Opportunity will be funded at OSC’s discretion through AmeriCorps Formula Funds. Funding is dedicated to establishing new and expanding existing programs in OSC’s AmeriCorps Grant Program portfolio. If awarded, OSC would provide specialized training and technical assistance to Applicants in order to help them better prepare to apply for a full AmeriCorps program grant.<br></div><p><br></p></div></dd><dt>Deadline to Apply</dt><dd>On a rolling basis, final deadline: 11/23/2025 at 11:59 PM</dd><dt>Review all Requirements</dt><dd><div class="ExternalClass8996C70E016D4917BD0A6771E6F6A3CD"><p>Please review all requirements in the RFA&#58;<br></p><p><a href="/highered/about/Documents/Grants-contracts/RFA/25-161-RFA%20OSC%20AmeriCorps%20Planning%20Grant%2025-26/25-161-RFA%20OSC%20AmeriCorps%20Planning%20Grant%2025-26%20Final.pdf">25-161-RFA OSC AmeriCorps Planning Grant 25-26 Final.pdf</a>​<br><br></p><div>Applications must be submitted via SMApply.&#160; I​nstructions to submit via SM Apply&#58;<br></div><div><br></div></div><blockquote style="margin&#58;0px 0px 0px 40px;border&#58;none;padding&#58;0px;"><div class="ExternalClass8996C70E016D4917BD0A6771E6F6A3CD"><div>• Go to&#58; <a href="https&#58;//oregonhecc.smapply.us/prog/2025-2026_oregonserves_americorps_planning_grant_application/">https&#58;//oregonhecc.smapply.us/prog/2025-2026_oregonserves_americorps_planning_grant_Application/&#160;​</a></div></div><div class="ExternalClass8996C70E016D4917BD0A6771E6F6A3CD"><div>• Click Apply.</div></div><div class="ExternalClass8996C70E016D4917BD0A6771E6F6A3CD"><div>• If you already have an account, log in, or register for an account.</div></div><div class="ExternalClass8996C70E016D4917BD0A6771E6F6A3CD"><div>• Click Start Application</div></div><div class="ExternalClass8996C70E016D4917BD0A6771E6F6A3CD"><div>• If you encounter any issues with SM Apply, please email oregon.serves@hecc.oregon.gov</div></div></blockquote><div class="ExternalClass8996C70E016D4917BD0A6771E6F6A3CD"><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div></dd><dt>Support</dt><dd><div class="ExternalClassB6164A1ED68B4F6DBC36A1468E27AEA3"><p>​</p><div>Single Point of Contact (“SPC”)&#58; Matthew Collins</div><div>Email&#58; oregon.serves@hecc.oregon.gov ​<br></div><p><br></p></div></dd>
						</dl>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div><div class="ms-clear"></div></div>
</div>
</div></div><div id="vid_582311c0-e0e0-4b19-9250-59a61fa0f0c7" unselectable="on" style="display&#58;none;"></div></div><hr class="additional-block" /></div>
		</div>
	</div>

